T02TD1332E:293b-1: shr'i ratna bindu n'a ma s'a dha nam no pi ka / bod skad du /
T02TD1332E:293b-2: dpal rin chen thigs pa zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD1332E:293b-3: dpal bde ba chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1332E:293b-4: bde chen yan lag ma dang ldan //
T02TD1332E:293b-5: rang nyid bde ba chen po yin //
T02TD1332E:293b-6: bde ba chen po'i gnas na bzhugs //
T02TD1332E:293b-7: he ru ka dpal bdag phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1332E:293b-8: skal ldan rnams kyi grub don du //
T02TD1332E:293b-9: mdor bsdus pa yi sgrub thabs bshad //
T02TD1332E:293b-10: dang por rnal 'byor dbang phyug gis //
T02TD1332E:293b-11: rab tu sbyor ba 'di gnas bya //
T02TD1332E:293b-13: de las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ro //
T02TD1332E:293b-15: de las me yi dkyil 'khor ro //
T02TD1332E:293b-17: rlung gis me ni bteg par bya //
T02TD1332E:293b-18: bha ga'i padma'i nang du ni //
T02TD1332E:293b-19: yang dag par ni 'bar bar bsgom //
T02TD1332E:293b-20: 'bar ba'i me yis lus kun gyi //
T02TD1332E:293b-21: rtog pa'i bdag nyid bsreg par bya //
T02TD1332E:293b-24: 'od du zhu ba'i bdud rtsi ni //
T02TD1332E:293b-25: srog gi rtsa ba'i nang nas 'bab //
T02TD1332E:293b-26: rgyun ni mi 'chad pa yis ni //
T02TD1332E:293b-27: sngar tshig pa ni rab tshim bya //
T02TD1332E:293b-28: rang lus ye shes bdag nyid ni //
T02TD1332E:293b-29: mi bskyod pa yi gzugs su mthong //
T02TD1332E:293b-30: aom sva bh'a wa shuddha: sarba dharm'a: sva bh'a ba shuddho& ham /
T02TD1332E:293b-31: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham //
T02TD1332E:293b-33: 'khor lo dang ldan he ru bdag / gru gsum phyag rgya dbus kyi gnas //
T02TD1332E:293b-34: nyi ma'i steng na gar dang ldan //
T02TD1332E:293b-35: zhal bzhi pa la phyag brgyad pa //
T02TD1332E:293b-36: chu skyes sngon po'i gzugs dang ldan //
T02TD1332E:293b-37: spyan gsum pa la g-yas brkyang ba //
T02TD1332E:293b-38: legs skyes dbang phyug mas ni 'khyud //
T02TD1332E:293b-39: thod rlon phreng ba'i do shal can //
T02TD1332E:293b-40: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od dang mnyam //
T02TD1332E:293b-41: mi bskyod pa yis dbu la brgyan //
T02TD1332E:293b-42: phyag rgya drug gis yan lag brgyan //
T02TD1332E:293b-43: thod pa'i phreng bas dbu la brgyan //
T02TD1332E:293b-44: gtsug tor zla ba phyed pa can //
T02TD1332E:293b-45: gnag dang ser dang dmar dang ljang //
T02TD1332E:293b-46: g-yon nas bskor pa'i zhal dang ldan //
T02TD1332E:293b-47: 'khyud pa'i phyag ni g-yas pa na //
T02TD1332E:293b-48: rdo rje dang ni dril bu g-yon //
T02TD1332E:293b-49: nyi ma mda' dang ka p'a la //
T02TD1332E:293b-50: g-yas pa yi ni phyag na bsnams //
T02TD1332E:293b-51: zla ba gzhu dang kha tv'am ga / g-yon pa yi ni phyag na bsnams //
T02TD1332E:293b-52: legs dgyes dbang mo de dang mthun //
T02TD1332E:293b-53: yang na phyag ni gnyis par dran //
T02TD1332E:293b-54: phyag ni gri gug ka p'a la //
T02TD1332E:294a-3: gnyis su med pa'i gnas na bzhugs //
T02TD1332E:294a-4: legs dgyes ma dang rdor 'tsho ma //
T02TD1332E:294a-5: de bzhin rdo rje glang chen ma //
T02TD1332E:294a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal dang mthun //
T02TD1332E:294a-7: gru gsum la ni bsgom bya ste //
T02TD1332E:294a-8: zhal gcig pa la spyan gsum pa //
T02TD1332E:294a-9: zhal bzhi pa la g-yon brkyang gnas //
T02TD1332E:294a-10: gla rtsi gur kum ga pur gyis //
T02TD1332E:294a-11: bkang ba'i ka p'a la rnams ni //
T02TD1332E:294a-12: sgeg pa'i phyag ni gnyis na thogs //
T02TD1332E:294a-13: gru gsum phyag rgya spyi bor gzhag / mdzub mo gnyis ni 'og tu'o //
T02TD1332E:294a-14: skra grol ba la gcer bu ste //
T02TD1332E:294a-15: thod rlon do shal gyis brgyan pa //
T02TD1332E:294a-17: phyag rgya lnga yis yan lag brgyan //
T02TD1332E:294a-18: la la n'a sogs dag par ni //
T02TD1332E:294a-19: bsgrub pa'i dbang pos shes par bya //
T02TD1332E:294a-20: de nas bde chen 'khor lo bzhir //
T02TD1332E:294a-21: padma'i snod kyi nang du ni //
T02TD1332E:294a-22: bdud rtsi lnga ni lha yi mchog / de bzhin gshegs pa lnga'i bdag nyid //
T02TD1332E:294a-23: char yang steng nas ye shes me //
T02TD1332E:294a-24: de yi 'og gi rlung dang ni //
T02TD1332E:294a-25: gnyis su sbyor bas me 'bar ba //
T02TD1332E:294a-26: de yis bdud rtsi zhu byas te //
T02TD1332E:294a-27: rdor gsum ye shes sa bon gyis //
T02TD1332E:294a-28: dkar byas rtogs byas 'bar byas so //
T02TD1332E:294a-29: sngags kyi byin gyi rlabs kyis ni //
T02TD1332E:294a-30: dang lce padma'i 'dab mar gzhag / phyi nang bdag nyid can gyi gzugs //
T02TD1332E:294a-31: 'khor lo de yis rab tshim bya //
T02TD1332E:294a-32: aom yo ga aa mri ta shuddha: sarba dharma yo ga aa mri ta shuddho nyaham //
T02TD1332E:294a-33: de nas mgon po'i snying po ni //
T02TD1332E:294a-34: thams cad grub pa'i don du bzlas //
T02TD1332E:294a-35: aom badzra te tso gra hrim hrim h'um phat //
T02TD1332E:294a-36: aom glim blim dzlim phat sv'a h'a //
T02TD1332E:294a-37: aom badzra s'a ga ri h'um phat /
T02TD1332E:294a-38: aom badzra su ra ta h'um phat /
T02TD1332E:294a-39: aom badzra ku nydza ri h'um phat /
T02TD1332E:294a-40: gru gsum gnas pa'i rnal 'byor ma //
T02TD1332E:294a-41: mchod pa'i dus su mchod par bya //
T02TD1332E:294a-42: de nas gtor ma sbyin par bya //
T02TD1332E:294a-43: sems can rnams la bsrung pa'i phyir //
T02TD1332E:294a-44: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dha rm'a n'am a'adya nutpann tv'ata aom a'a: h'um phat sv'a h'a //
T02TD1332E:294a-45: de nas rnal 'byor ngal bso bya //
T02TD1332E:294a-46: steng dang 'og ni spangs pa yin //
T02TD1332E:294a-47: gnas su gting rings dbus su ni //
T02TD1332E:294a-48: rang rig shes rab ldan pa yin //
T02TD1332E:294a-49: drug cu rtsa bzhi 'dab ma'i nang //
T02TD1332E:294a-50: yang dag dri med ma sres cha //
T02TD1332E:294a-51: de yi dbus su mchog gi tshul //
T02TD1332E:294a-52: dri med rnam dag gnyis la khyab //
T02TD1332E:294a-53: rang dngos rdzogs pa de ni mthong //
T02TD1332E:294b-0: @294b bskyed pa dang ni rdzogs pa med //
T02TD1332E:294b-1: rlabs med pa yi rang bzhin no //
T02TD1332E:294b-2: rlangs med pa yi sems kyis ni //
T02TD1332E:294b-3: mchog gi dngos po rnyed pa yin //
T02TD1332E:294b-4: de la cung zad blta ru med //
T02TD1332E:294b-5: de ni dpal me'i zhal snga yi //
T02TD1332E:294b-6: zhal gyi padma mchog las ni //
T02TD1332E:294b-7: au rgyan yul nas bdag gis rnyed //
T02TD1332E:294b-9: phyi nas rang gi dran don du //
T02TD1332E:294b-10: de yi tshig ni bris pa yin //
T02TD1332E:294b-11: rnal 'byor ma rnams bzod par mdzod //
T02TD1332E:294b-12: rin chen thigs pa zhes bya ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug dpal shes rab gsang bas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
